id=nh-batch6-usb-serial
name=NetHunter Batch6 USB Serial + Modems
version=v1.0
versionCode=1
author=ilyamen
description=USB Serial drivers (FTDI, CH341, PL2303, CP210x, OPTION, Qualcomm) + USB CDC ACM + cellular modems (Huawei NCM, QMI WWAN) + USB Printer host. Auto-loads at boot. Plug your FTDI/Arduino/USB-modem and it just works. Disable via Magisk Manager to unload.
